MyAction is a Form
    Layout
        three column
            PfiWorkunit
            PfiActivity
            PfiQueueAssignment
        blank line
        two column
            PfiMetrics.PfiUserProfile
            text of "<PfiMetrics.PfiUserProfile.FirstNameAndLastNameOrActor>"
        single column
            PfiMetrics.PfiTask
                compact format
        three column
            PfiActivity.ActivityName
            ActionTaken
            ActionDate
        blank line
